    public abstract class ModuleBasedConfiguration<ConfigurationModule extends RunConfigurationModule,T>
extends LocatableConfigurationBase<T>
implements java.lang.Cloneable, ModuleRunConfiguration
    Base class for a configuration that is associated with a specific module. For example, Java run configurations use the selected module to determine the run classpath.
